lead_paragraph: Jordin Canada knew in the third quarter she was inching closer to a second consecutive triple-double. Her teammates couldn't deliver it for her.

headline.print_headline: Canada Leads No. 9 UCLA Women to 80-64 Blowout of Cal Poly
